    "title": "Miniklub is Hiring: E-commerce Executive (Junior)",
    "description": "Join the Miniklub family as a E-commerce Executive in Hyderabad. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Miniklub:\nMiniklub is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Hyderabad, Telangana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Miniklub!",
